name: Natural Emotion (semeru volcanic eruption)
description:
Natural Emotions is a series of projects that reread nature or landscapes in the digital age, where they can all be enjoyed from a screen. Mount Semeru is the highest active volcano on the island of Java, Indonesia. Currently, Mount Semeru is erupting, which has a major impact on life and the surrounding ecosystem.

This work is part of a charity to help victims of the natural disaster from Mount Semeru eruption, every sale in the first market will be 100% donated to the victims, through sewon NFT. #tezos4semeru 


3000 x 2260 px
